Download from here https://github.com/haephrati/Secured-Globe-DVR/raw/master/SGDesktopVideoRecorder.exe
Use CTRL+SHIFT+Z to start capturing.
Change source : 
- CTRL+SHIFT+0 - Desktop capturing
- CTRL+SHIFT+<camera number> - Capture any connected camera.
CTRL+SHIFT+S - Capture a still image.
CTRL+SHIFT+M - Mute / Unmute sound recording.
